Temple cat in Amanohashidate, Japan. Photo by Nevin Thompson.

If you're looking for a new place to discover cats on the Internet, check out
the “Backstreet Cats of Japan” ( _Roji-ura Nyankichi_ , 路地裏のにゃん吉), an
[Instagram account](https://www.instagram.com/nyankichi5656/?hl=en) with over
100,000 followers.

The anonymous photographer has befriended and taken thousands of snapshots of
stray cats from an undisclosed location in Japan.

